<plot>Outlaws Slim Stevens (Donald Curtis) and Hutch Dalton (Tristram Coffin) are amazed to see gold nuggets fall out of Cannonball's pockets one day in the frontier town of Crestview. They force Cannonball (Dub Taylor) to reveal the location of a gold mine he has discovered. Slim, Hutch and their gang members make a beeline for the location, and trespass on the ranch of Big Bill Bailey (Jack Baxley) in doing so. Bailey and his foreman Bob Wilson (Bob Wills) put up a fight but are losing when Sheriff Lucky Crandall (Russell Hayden) arrives and helps drive off the outlaws, but not before one of Bailey's men has been killed. Madge Duncan (Alma Carroll), Slim's sister, learns of the killing and refuses to let her brother hide in her home. The gang plans an ambush for Lucky, but Lucky has some plans of his own involving a counter-ambush.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?017296</url></doc>
